        "\n",
        "### The MA(q) as an Infinite Autoregression\n",
        "\n",
        "Just as the AR($p$) has an MA($\\infty$) representation, an invertible MA($q$) has\n",
        "an AR($\\infty$) representation. Inverting $\\theta(L)$ when all its roots are inside\n",
        "the unit circle:\n",
